name: Addressbook
tagline: A Java developer API to create address books.
body:
### Welcome to the AddressBook API's website.
This project provides a Java API that could be used to create address books. The API is generalized to allow for it to be the back-end of clients or GUIs that may have rich features or specific data access optimizations to match user needs.

### Authors and Contributors
This API was written by Ken Luy (@tmnt-raphael).

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with the API? Check out the API's [README](https://github.com/tmnt-raphael/AddressBook/blob/master/README.md) or [Javadoc](http://tmnt-raphael.github.io/AddressBook/Javadoc.html).
